Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风在说着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奢华糕点 百万石馒头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.25,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}这里恶搞琦玉名点「十万石馒头」的CM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么芽间会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}超强怨念 被虐杀婆婆的怨灵袭向无情义的儿媳! !
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为世上还有心愿未了所以不能成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这个想法是比较合理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我所认识的芽间不管何时…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢这种丑八怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想向芽间道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不止是低头认错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事情我还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说不定这也是芽间的愿望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望仁碳去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校…

Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?  怎么突然想去上学了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 就是想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强自己比较好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前还是你叫我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前看齐～!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是仁碳的表情好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷得一干二净!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 也依靠一下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的妈妈已经成佛了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛…到底是怎么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常心 平常心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我心中一切皆无 无 无
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一脸没事的样子来学校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是那谁吧 一年三班的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 安城鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:12.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我都说了 果然是那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:12.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 安城?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫做大失所望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有几个人注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直没来的那家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 还被校长叫过去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽大意了吧 鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love Hotel什么的其实没什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城完胜了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样的话 之前拼命做的准备都白费了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说被PTA的人看到了呢 男的还是个大叔的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:49.11,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}PTA: Parent-Teacher Association 家长教师协会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援交?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家回到座位上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城你也赶快回到座位上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 请大家翻开课本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了啊 鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事中说的「我」的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着这样几种愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先第一种是 对「他」和「妻子」的背叛感到的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候安城还做笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.47,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}身为和丈夫亲密无间的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.41,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}却给「我」深爱的妻子写了信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:55.59,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}其次 怀有共同秘密的二人在信中使用了密码进行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙从小时候开始就这样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子不好 掌握不好要领
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺能干的嘛 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定跟她说一下 我们也可以「那啥」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}「我」作为男人的自尊心严重受创
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.69,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\frz219.944\pos(1090,404)}不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.69,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(782,291)\frz217.875}根本没做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.69,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(672,353)\frz280.075}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1028,179)\frz327.529}别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz35.206\pos(1177,283)}!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz326.706\pos(562,212)}给我永远闭上嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz38.14\pos(837,323)}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz329.486\pos(361,383)}去死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.90,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz33.154\pos(488,413)}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后第二种是对自己的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.70,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(1038,425,1071,431)\frz106.17}别擅自认定!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.70,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz99.371\move(636,255,669,261)}救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了信的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让「他」看到自己作为男人 作为丈夫的优越性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我」交给了妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援交?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也可以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援交 援交…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是那么久都没来学校的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有入学指导…最开始的一周来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 这脸很少见吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「撵」?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你是…宿海君?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙你们不是何时何地都能见着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LovHo?  这种事情值得闹那么大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.96,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}LovHo: Love Hotel的简称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不管怎么看 都像是去过LovHo好几次的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的LovHo脸吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这家伙 是绝对不会搞援交的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这家伙还是A型血 山羊座 和冒险无缘的正经相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼镜总板着脸爱惜物品喜欢收拾整理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小开始就喜欢收集各种小东西 戴着眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是无聊到死的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那么多废话!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 拿上书包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一…下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然喊「看着我吧」 不管怎么想都是变态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你替我出头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我决不是LovHo脸!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没去LovHo嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没进去过!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好了好了」那算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 总之先回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈也在担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校肯定已经跟家里联系过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会被骂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人绝对不会原谅这种事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也不能这样啊…

Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.04,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(692,555)}第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.04,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(656,638)}忘记 别忘记

Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 说什么要在这里住 安鸣你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要等这阵风过去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵风…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是凝聚了我的汗水泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他各种男人体液的我的城堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是大家一起建的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是证据啊 看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刻上去的哈姆太郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆太郎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是火腿 不如说是烤肠?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.05,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}哈姆和火腿同音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 你那男人体液太臭了 要打扫干净再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等下 别碰那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这是啥! 都腐烂了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说要住下来 不跟老妈说一声的话还是有问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情会闹得更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她胆子小嘛 总是藏在芽间的身后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在芽间人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 要去芽间家里看看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不准可以找出什么实现芽间愿望的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮我 实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 只是想带上芽间一起去比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 她在的话 说「去芽间家里」什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得不太合适吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然意外地会做人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 我毕竟在越南获得了萨满五级的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这样定了的话 也给雪集他们发邮件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…地址地址
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.28,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.826\pos(519,551)}快定期测验了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.28,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.826\pos(631,583)}今天会很晚放学所以去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.28,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.826\pos(531,644)}鹤见也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 这么冷酷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点高中就是那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 本来我还在想 大家那么久没见 居然都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不可能的啊 一点点地在变着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 还是不要去芽间家里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来就没有去芽间家里玩过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…因为芽间她爸很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 说不定是个好机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我也想给芽间烧烧香什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去了的话 芽间的妈妈会是什么表情呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 大家居然都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子肯定也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 进来进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去和芽衣子打个招呼怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在动摇什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我本来就清楚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是芽衣子的房间 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 鹤见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈子想让你把这个交给松雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正同一个班 自己交给他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 鹤见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为一直在他身边就比我们强吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见你喜欢松雪君的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了吗?  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这附近有奇怪的家伙出没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是像那样被人妒忌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的女装照片发过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不好一下子就能解决这烦恼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来宿海他们 好像要去芽间家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都把宿海说的话当真了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明大家都没办法真的把过去当作过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以松雪集这个人为首呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变老实了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你面前的话 不管怎么解释都没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不爽 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是所在高中的水平 还是这样那样的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明现在都是我比他高出许多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是和那时候一样 被那家伙随意摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在居然连芽间的名字都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底要把别人玩弄到什么地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是他说要到秘密基地集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…好像是芽间提出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对 被芽间打电话叫出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 那天 她好像说要商量什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间说有事要和大家商量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间的日记 居然这么容易就借到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太冷清了 房间弄成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸爸说 不能一直被芽衣子所束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就把这间屋子收拾了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…芽衣子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到原本的房间 会更痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做妈妈的心情 我是不太理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她肯定把自己孩子的一切 看得比什么都要重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先回家一趟好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是怕家里人担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想起有些事情必须要做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不老实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 日记拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去秘密基地慢慢研读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可以等下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 今天该我做晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且早上的盘子都还没洗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先读了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不在的时候先不要看 绝对不要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了反而更痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:18:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 看不到芽间反而更好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:16.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}仁碳 欢迎回来 学上得怎样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…反而更…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢…就随他们一起去了 见到了你妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收! 没收!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话 妈妈又要想起芽间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让妈妈很寂寞很寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不想再让妈妈更寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再让妈妈想起我的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让她想起来是不可能的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那么一点都好…也希望妈妈能把我忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说谎了 你不是说了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没把你忘了让你很高兴什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧你!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样只考虑别人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多考虑一下自己的事情啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人不爽啊 你那态度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很难过 却还强颜欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭的都是为别人而哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…我会这么愤怒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻血!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快塞纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸巾!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后仰头躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话慢慢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间出去?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我在干什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?  都这个时间了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你才是 不是回家了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你那样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的 这是刚才残留下来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是对你有什么非分之想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来! 变态!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H! Sketch! One touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.19,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}N年前流行于日本的一句押韵文 用来形容变态的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的…那家伙绝对是处女…

Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:35.30,ed_jp_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}出会いは　ふっとした　瞬間　帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:41.27,ed_jp_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}声をかけてくれたね　「一緒に帰ろう」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:49.86,ed_jp_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}あぁ　花火が夜空　きれいに咲いて　ちょっとセツナク
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:56.11,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}あぁ　風が時間とともに　流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.28,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}嬉しくって　楽しくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.87,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}冒険も　いろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:10.66,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}二人の　秘密の　基地の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:11.64,ed_jp_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}君と夏の終わり　将来の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:15.00,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}君と夏の終わり　将来の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:18.17,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}大きな希望　忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.10,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}10年後の8月　また出会えるのを　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:28.55,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}君が最後まで　心から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:32.39,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}「ありがとう」叫んでいたこと　知ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:39.44,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}涙をこらえて　笑顔でさようなら　せつないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:48.95,ed_jp_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}最高の想い出を...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:35.30,ed_cn_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}相遇就在不经意的瞬间  站在归途的交叉路口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:41.27,ed_cn_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}你叫住了我 说了声「一起回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:49.86,ed_cn_formal_A,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}啊 烟花在夜空中 绚烂地绽放 却让人有些失落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:56.11,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}啊 风随着时间 一同流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.28,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}好兴奋 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.87,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}还记得那无数次的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:10.66,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}就在我们两人的秘密基地里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:11.64,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}在夏天的尾声 和你畅谈未来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:15.00,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}在夏天的尾声 和你畅谈未来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:18.17,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}一同许下的那个大大的愿望 又怎能遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.10,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}坚信着 10年后的8月 还会与你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:28.55,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}我知道 直到分别前的最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:32.39,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,200)}你仍真心呼喊着说「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:39.44,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我知道 忍住泪水微笑着说再见 有多心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:48.95,ed_cn_formal_B,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份最难忘的回忆…
